    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold"><Petapetual /> for late friends</h1>

    <p>
        Losing a close friend is a unique kind of pain. It’s a profound loss
        that can shake you to your core. Friends are the family we choose, and
        their absence leaves a very specific silence. You find yourself missing
        the inside jokes, the easy companionship, and the person who understood
        you in a way that few others do.
    </p>

    <p>
        In the midst of that sadness, a powerful need emerges: the desire to
        honor them. We want to celebrate who they were, not just mourn their
        passing. You feel the pull to gather the photos, the shared memories,
        and the funny stories that perfectly capture their unique spirit. It’s a
        way to pay respects to the incredible life they lived and the special
        bond you shared.
    </p>

    <p>
        This need to share and remember is a vital part of grieving. It’s a way
        to keep their light going and to find a sense of community with others
        who are also feeling the loss. We need a place to put that love and
        reflect on the wonderful impact they had on all of our lives.
    </p>

    <p>
        At <Petapetual />, we understand how important that bond is. We created
        our online memorials to offer a peaceful, dedicated space where you can
        build a beautiful tribute to your friend. It’s a place to collect those
        cherished photos, write down the stories that make you smile, and invite
        other friends and family to share their own memories. It offers a
        central place for comfort and celebration, ensuring their unique legacy
        is preserved for everyone to visit, anytime.
    </p>
